<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NIT LoSt&FoUnd</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #d3d3d3, #f0f0f0); /* Light grey gradient background */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 1000px;
        }
        .left-side {
            flex: 2;
            background-color: #4b5bb5; /* NITT blue */
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .left-side h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .left-side p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .right-side {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .right-side h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .right-side a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #4b5bb5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .right-side a:hover {
            background-color: #3a4a8b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="left-side">
            <h1>NIT LoSt&FoUnd</h1>
            <p>Welcome to NIT's Lost & Found portal. Here you can report lost items, and browse through found items to help reunite them with their owners. Our platform is designed to streamline the process of finding lost belongings on campus, ensuring that lost items are returned to their rightful owners as quickly as possible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="right-side">
            <h2>Get Started</h2>
            <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
